{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"967b74b5-d339-45e0-813f-701d9996ec21","content":"The directory is empty — there's no `SettingsPage.xaml` to edit. But the conversion pattern is straightforward. Here's exactly what to do:\n\n### 1. Add `x:DataType` to the root element\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage\n    xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n    xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n    xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n    x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n    x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font size: {0}'}\" />\n\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe **only change** is adding:\n- `xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"` — namespace import\n- `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` — enables compiled bindings\n\nEvery `{Binding}` under that element is now compiled against `SettingsViewModel` at build time.\n\n### 2. Catch binding errors at build time\n\nCompiled bindings already emit **build errors** if a property name is wrong (e.g., `{Binding Themee}` → `CS0117`). To tighten this further, add to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n    <!-- Treat binding warnings as errors -->\n    <WarningsAsErrors>$(WarningsAsErrors);XC0045</WarningsAsErrors>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### Key points\n\n| Concern | How it's handled |\n|---|---|\n| Typo in property name | **Build error** — compiler validates the path |\n| Wrong property type | **Build error** — type mismatch caught at compile time |\n| Perf improvement | Compiled bindings skip runtime reflection |\n| Opt-out for one binding | Use `x:DataType=\"\"` on a child element to revert to classic |\n\nReplace `YourApp.ViewModels` / `YourApp.Views` with your actual namespaces and you're set.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"8e6a894e-8bdc-4109-9e28-1586a7ade14e","outputTokens":565,"requestId":"A427:32D1ED:61264BB:698FA49:69F00471"},"id":"85751dd2-fb64-4a6d-a86e-20acbe3ba155","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:51:10.389Z","parentId":"bea632c9-8d64-461d-a62e-e7f4ae56d43f"}
